\c 7
\s Zvipiriso zvinopiwa paaritari
\p
\v 1 Zvino zvakaitika nezuva Mozisi raakapedza naro kumisa tabhenakeri, uye aizodza, uye aiita tsvene nenhumbi dzayo dzese, nearitari nemidziyo yayo yese, uye azvizodza nekuzviita zvitsvene,
\v 2 kuti machinda eVaIsraeri, misoro yedzimba dzemadzibaba avo, vaiva machinda emarudzi uye vaiva vatariri pavari ivo vakaverengwa;
\v 3 ndokuuya nezvipo zvavo pamberi paJehovha, ngoro nhanhatu dzakafukidzwa, nenzombe gumi nembiri, ngoro imwe yemachinda maviri, uye nzombe pane umwe; ndokuuya nazvo pamberi petabhenakeri.
\v 4 Zvino Jehovha wakataura kuna Mozisi achiti:
\v 5 Gamuchira kwavari, kuti zvive zvekubata basa retende rekusangana uye uchazvipa kuVaRevhi, kune umwe neumwe zvichienderana nebasa rake.
\v 6 Naizvozvo Mozisi wakagamuchira ngoro nenzombe ndokuzvipa kuVaRevhi.
\v 7 Ngoro mbiri nenzombe ina wakapa kuvanakomana vaGerishoni zvichienderana nebasa ravo.
\v 8 Zvino ngoro ina nenzombe sere wakapa kuvanakomana vaMerari zvichienderana nebasa ravo, paruoko rwaItamari, mwanakomana waAroni mupristi.
\v 9 Asi kuvanakomana vaKohati haana kupa, nokuti basa renzvimbo tsvene raiva pamusoro pavo, vautakure pamafudzi avo.
\p
\v 10 Machinda akapa zvipo zvekutsaurwa kwearitari nezuva rayakazodzwa naro, nemachinda akapa zvipo zvawo pamberi pearitari.
\v 11 Zvino Jehovha wakati kuna Mozisi: muchinda umwe neumwe nezuva rake, vachapa zvipo zvavo zvekutsaurira aritari.
\p
\v 12 Neanopa chipo chake zuva rekutanga waiva Naashoni, mwanakomana waAminadhabhu, werudzi rwaJudha.
\v 13 Zvino chipo chake \add chaiva\add* zindiro rimwe resirivha, kurema kwaro mashekeri zana nemakumi matatu, ndiro yekusasa imwe yesirivha yemashekeri makumi manomwe, zvichienderana neshekeri reimba tsvene; zvese zviviri zvizere neupfu hwakatsetseka hwakakanyiwa nemafuta, chive chipo chechidyiwa;
\v 14 mukombe umwe wegoridhe ye\add mashekeri\add* gumi, uzere nezvipfungaidzo zvinonhuhwira,
\v 15 handira imwe mwana wemombe gondobwe rimwe, gwayana rimwe regore rimwe, chive chipo chinopiswa,
\v 16 nhongo imwe yembudzi, chive chipo chezvivi;
\v 17 uye zvechipo chekuyananisa, nzombe mbiri, makondobwe mashanu, nhongo shanu dzembudzi, makwayana mashanu egore rimwe; ichi chipo chaNaashoni, mwanakomana waAminadhabhu.
\p
\v 18 Nezuva repiri Netaneri, mwanakomana waZuari, muchinda waIsaskari wakapa chipo chake.
\v 19 Wakapa chipo chake: Zindiro rimwe resirivha, kurema kwaro \add mashekeri\add* zana nemakumi matatu, nendiro yekusasa imwe yesirivha yemashekeri makumi manomwe, zvichienderana neshekeri reimba tsvene; zvese zviviri zvizere neupfu hwakatsetseka, hwakakanyiwa nemafuta, chive chipo chechidyiwa;
\v 20 mukombe umwe wegoridhe re\add mashekeri\add* gumi, uzere nezvipfungaidzo zvinonhuhwira,
\v 21 handira duku imwe mhuru yemombe, gondobwe rimwe, gwayana rimwe regore rimwe, chive chipo chinopiswa;
\v 22 mbudzana imwe yembudzi, chive chipo chezvivi;
\v 23 uye zvechibairo chechipo chekuyananisa, nzombe mbiri, makondobwe mashanu, nhongo shanu dzembudzi, makwayana mashanu egore rimwe; ichi chipo chaNetaneri, mwanakomana waZuari.
\p
\v 24 Nezuva retatu \add kwakauya\add* Eriabhu mwanakomana waHeroni muchinda wevana vaZebhuruni.
\v 25 Chipo chake \add chaiti\add*: Zindiro rimwe resirivha, kurema kwaro \add mashekeri\add* zana nemakumi matatu, ndiro imwe yekusasa wesirivha yemashekeri makumi manomwe, zvichienderana neshekeri reimba tsvene; zvese zviviri zvizere neupfu hwakatsetseka, hwakakanyiwa nemafuta chive chipo chechidyiwa;
\v 26 mukombe umwe wegoridhe we\add mashekeri\add* gumi, uzere nezvipfungaidzo zvinonhuhwira,
\v 27 handira diki imwe, gondobwe rimwe, gwayana rimwe regore rimwe, chive chipo chinopiswa;
\v 28 mbudzana imwe yembudzi, chive chipo chezvivi;
\v 29 nezvechiairo chechipo chekuyananisa, nzombe mbiri, makondobwe mashanu, nhongo shanu dzembudzi, makwayana mashanu egore rimwe; ichi chipo chaEriabhu, mwanakomana waHeroni.
\p
\v 30 Nezuva rechina \add kwakauya\add* Erizuri, mwanakomana waShedheuri, muchinda wevana vaRubheni.
\v 31 Chipo chake chaiti: Ndiro imwe huru yesirivha, kurema kwayo kwakange kuri mashekeri ane zana namakumi matatu, nomudziyo umwe wesirivha wamashekeri ana makumi manomwe, zvichienzaniswa neshekeri reimba tsvene; zvese zviri zviviri zvakange zvizere noupfu hwakatsetseka, hwakakanyiwa namafuta, chive chipo choupfu;
\v 32 nendiro imwe yegoridhe yamashekeri ane gumi, izere nezvinonhuhwira,
\v 33 nenzombe imwe, negondobwe rimwe, negwayana rimwe regondobwe regore rimwe, chive chipo chinopiswa;
\v 34 nenhongo imwe yembudzi, chive chipo chezvivi;
\v 35 nenzombe mbiri, namakondobwe mashanu, nenhongo shanu dzembudzi, namakwayana mashanu amakondobwe egore rimwe, chive chibairo chezvipiriso zvokuyananisa; ndicho chaiva chipo chaErizuri, mwanakomana waShedheuri.
\p
\v 36 Nezuva reshanu Sherumieri, mwanakomana waZurishadhai, muchinda wavana vaSimioni, akauya.
\v 37 Chipo chake chaiti: Ndiro imwe huru yesirivha, kurema kwayo kwakange kuri mashekeri ane zana namakumi matatu, nomudziyo umwe wesirivha wamashekeri ana makumi manomwe, zvichienzaniswa neshekeri reimba tsvene; zvese zviri zviviri zvakange zvizere noupfu hwakatsetseka, hwakakanyiwa namafuta, chive chipo choupfu;
\v 38 nendiro imwe yegoridhe yamashekeri ane gumi, izere nezvinonhuhwira,
\v 39 nenzombe imwe, negondobwe rimwe, negwayana rimwe regondobwe regore rimwe, chive chipo chinopiswa;
\v 40 nenhongo imwe yembudzi, chive chipo chezvivi;
\v 41 nenzombe mbiri, namakondobwe mashanu, nenhongo shanu dzembudzi, namakwayana mashanu amakondobwe egore rimwe, chive chibairo chezvipiriso zvokuyananisa; ndicho chaiva chipo chaSherumieri, mwanakomana waZurishadhai.
\p
\v 42 Nezuva retanhatu Eriasafi, mwanakomana waDheueri, muchinda wavana vaGadhi, akauya.
\v 43 Chipo chake chaiti: Ndiro imwe huru yesirivha, kurema kwayo kwakange kuri mashekeri ane zana namakumi matatu, nomudziyo umwe wesirivha wamashekeri ana makumi manomwe, zvichienzaniswa neshekeri reimba tsvene; zvese zviri zviviri zvizere noupfu hwakatsetseka, hwakakanyiwa namafuta, chive chipo choupfu,
\v 44 nendiro imwe yegoridhe yamashekeri ane gumi, izere nezvinonhuhwira,
\v 45 nenzombe imwe, negondobwe rimwe, negwayana rimwe regondobwe regore rimwe, chive chipo chinopiswa;
\v 46 nenhongo imwe yembudzi, chive chipo chezvivi;
\v 47 nenzombe mbiri, namakondobwe mashanu, nenhongo shanu dzembudzi, namakwayana mashanu amakondobwe egore rimwe, chive chibairo chezvipiriso zvokuyananisa; ndicho chaiva chipo chaEriasafi, mwanakomana waDheueri.
\p
\v 48 Nezuva rechinomwe Erishama, mwanakomana waAmihudhi, muchinda wavana vaEfuremu, akauya.
\v 49 Chipo chake chaiti: Ndiro imwe huru yesirivha, kurema kwayo kwakange kuri mashekeri ane zana namakumi matatu, nomudziyo umwe wesirivha wamashekeri ana makumi manomwe, zvichienzaniswa neshekeri reimba tsvene; zvese zviri zviviri zvakange zvizere noupfu hwakatsetseka, hwakakanyiwa namafuta, chive chipo choupfu;
\v 50 nendiro imwe yegoridhe yamashekeri ane gumi, izere nezvinonhuhwira,
\v 51 nenzombe imwe, negondobwe rimwe, negwayana rimwe regondobwe regore rimwe, chive chipo chinopiswa;
\v 52 nenhongo imwe yembudzi, chive chipo chezvivi;
\v 53 nenzombe mbiri, namakondobwe mashanu, nenhongo shanu dzembudzi, namakwayana mashanu amakondobwe egore rimwe, chive chibairo chezvipiriso zvokuyananisa; ndicho chaiva chipo chaErishama, mwanakomana waAmihudhi.
\p
\v 54 Nezuva rorusere Gamarieri, mwanakomana waPedhazuri, muchinda wa vana vaManase, akauya.
\v 55 Chipo chake chaiti: Ndiro imwe huru yesirivha, kurema kwayo kwakange kuri mashekeri ane zana namakumi matatu, nomudziyo umwe wesirivha wamashekeri ana makumi manomwe, zvichienzaniswa neshekeri reimba tsvene; zvese zviri zviviri zvakange zvizere noupfu hwakatsetseka, hwakakanyiwa namafuta, chive chipo choupfu;
\v 56 nendiro imwe yegoridhe yamashekeri ane gumi, izere nezvinonhuhwira,
\v 57 nenzombe imwe, negondobwe rimwe, negwayana rimwe regondobwe regore rimwe, chive chipo chinopiswa;
\v 58 nenhongo imwe yembudzi, chive chipo chezvivi;
\v 59 nenzombe mbiri, namakondobwe mashanu, nenhongo shanu dzembudzi, namakwayana mashanu amakondobwe egore rimwe, chive chibairo chezvipiriso zvokuyananisa; ndicho chaiva chipo chaGamarieri, mwanakomana waPedhazuri.
\p
\v 60 Nezuva repfumbamwe Abhidhani, mwanakomana waGidheoni, muchinda wavana vaBhenjamini, akauya.
\v 61 Chipo chake chaiti: Ndiro imwe huru yesirivha, kurema kwayo kwakange kuri mashekeri ane zana namakumi matatu, nomudziyo umwe wesirivha wamashekeri ana makumi manomwe, zvichienzaniswa neshekeri reimba tsvene; zvese zviri zviviri zvakange zvizere noupfu hwakatsetseka, hwakakanyiwa namafuta, chive chipo choupfu;
\v 62 nendiro imwe yegoridhe ramashekeri ane gumi, izere nezvinonhuhwira,
\v 63 nenzombe imwe, negondobwe rimwe, negwayana rimwe regondobwe regore rimwe, chive chipo chinopiswa;
\v 64 nenhongo imwe yembudzi, chive chipo chezvivi;
\v 65 nenzombe mbiri, namakondobwe mashanu, nenhongo shanu dzembudzi, namakwayana mashanu amakondobwe egore rimwe, chive chibairo chezvipiriso zvokuyananisa; ndicho chaiva chipo chaAbhidhani, mwanakomana waGidheoni.
\p
\v 66 Nezuva regumi Ahiezeri, mwanakomana waAmishadhai, muchinda wavana vaDhani, akauya.
\v 67 Chipo chake chaiti: Ndiro imwe huru yesirivha, kurema kwayo kwakange kuri mashekeri ane zana namakumi matatu, nomudziyo umwe wesirivha wamashekeri ana makumi manomwe, zvichienzaniswa neshekeri reimba tsvene; zvese zviri zviviri zvakange zvizere noupfu hwakatsetseka, hwakakanyiwa namafuta, chive chipo choupfu;
\v 68 nendiro imwe yegoridhe ramashekeri ane gumi, izere nezvinonhuhwira,
\v 69 nenzombe imwe, negondobwe rimwe, negwayana rimwe regondobwe regore rimwe, chive chipo chinopiswa;
\v 70 nenhongo imwe yembudzi, chive chipo chezvivi;
\v 71 nenzombe mbiri, namakondobwe mashanu, nenhongo shanu dzembudzi, namakwayana mashanu amakondobwe egore rimwe, chive chibairo chezvipiriso zvokuyananisa; ndicho chaiva chipo chaAhiezeri, mwanakomana waAmishadhai.
\p
\v 72 Nezuva regumi nerimwe Pagieri, mwanakomana waOkirani, muchinda wavana vaAsheri, akauya.
\v 73 Chipo chake chaiti: Ndiro imwe huru yesirivha, kurema kwayo kwakange kuri mashekeri ane zana namakumi matatu, nomudziyo umwe wesirivha wamashekeri ana makumi manomwe, zvichienzaniswa neshekeri reimba tsvene; zvese zviri zviviri zvakange zvizere noupfu hwakatsetseka, hwakakanyiwa namafuta, chive chipo choupfu;
\v 74 nendiro imwe yegoridhe remashekeri ane gumi, izere nezvinonhuhwira,
\v 75 nenzombe imwe, negondobwe rimwe negwayana rimwe regondobwe regore rimwe, chive chipo chinopiswa;
\v 76 nenhongo imwe yembudzi, chive chipo chezvivi;
\v 77 nenzombe mbiri, namakondobwe mashanu, nenhongo shanu dzembudzi, namakwayana mashanu amakondobwe egore rimwe, chive chibairo chezvipiriso zvokuyananisa; ndicho chaiva chipo chaPagieri, mwanakomana waOkirani.
\p
\v 78 Nezuva regumi namaviri Ahira, mwanakomana waEnani, muchinda wavana vaNafutari, akauya.
\v 79 Chipo chake chaiti: Ndiro imwe huru yesirivha, kurema kwayo kwakange kuri mashekeri ane zana namakumi matatu, nomudziyo umwe wesirivha wamashekeri ana makumi manomwe, zvichienzaniswa neshekeri reimba tsvene; zvese zviri zviviri zvakange zvizere noupfu hwakatsetseka, hwakakanyiwa namafuta, chive chipo choupfu;
\v 80 nendiro imwe yegoridhe yemashekeri ane gumi, izere nezvinonhuhwira,
\v 81 nenzombe imwe, negondobwe rimwe, negwayana rimwe regondobwe regore rimwe, chive chipo chinopiswa,
\v 82 nenhongo imwe yembudzi, chive chipo chezvivi;
\v 83 nenzombe mbiri, namakondobwe mashanu, nenhongo shanu dzembudzi, namakwayana mashanu amakondobwe egore rimwe, chive chibairo chezvipiriso zvokuyananisa; ndicho chaiva chipo chaAhira, mwanakomana waEnani.
\p
\v 84 Ndicho chipo chokutsaurwa kwearitari nomusi wayakazodzwa nawo namachinda aIsraeri. Ndiro huru dzesirivha dzine gumi nembiri, nemidziyo yesirivha ine gumi nembiri, nendiro dzegoridhe dzine gumi nembiri;
\v 85 ndiro imwe huru yesirivha yakasvika mashekeri ane zana namakumi matatu, nomudziyo umwe neumwe mashekeri ana makumi manomwe; sirivha yese yemidziyo yese yakasvika mashekeri ane zvuru zviviri namazana mana, zvichienzaniswa neshekeri reimba tsvene;
\v 86 nendiro dzine gumi nembiri dzegoridhe, dzakange dzizere nezvinonhuhwira, imwe neimwe yakange ina mashekeri ane gumi, zvichienzaniswa neshekeri reimba tsvene; goridhe rese rendiro rakasvika mashekeri ane zana namakumi maviri;
\v 87 nzombe dzese dzezvipiriso zvinopiswa dzakasvika nzombe dzine gumi nembiri, namakondobwe ane gumi namaviri, namakwayana amakondobwe egore rimwe ane gumi namaviri, nezvipiriso zvazvo zvoupfu; nenhongo dzembudzi gumi nembiri, chive chipo chezvivi;
\v 88 nzombe dzese dzechibairo chezvipiriso zvokuyananisa dzakasvika nzombe dzina makumi maviri neina, namakondobwe ana makumi matanhatu, nenhongo dzembudzi dzina makumi matanhatu, namakwayana amakondobwe egore rimwe ana makumi matanhatu. Ndicho chipo chokutsaurwa kwearitari, shure kokuzodzwa kwayo.
\p
\v 89 Zvino Mozisi akati apinda mutende rokusangana, kuti ataure naye, akanzwa inzwi richitaura naye, richibva pachifunhiro chokuyananisa, chakange chiri pamusoro peareka yechipupuriro, richibva pakati pamakerubhi maviri; akataura naye.
